import React from 'react';
import CardDeck from 'react-bootstrap/CardDeck'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'

class Cards extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <CardDeck className="cardContent">
  <Card>
    <Card.Img  src="/USPHome.png" alt="uspimg" />
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Text className="customCard">
      USP Point 1
      </Card.Text>
    </Card.Body>

  </Card>
  <Card>
    <Card.Img variant="top" src={require("../USPHome.png")} alt="uspimg" />
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Text className="customCard">
        USP Point 2
      </Card.Text>
    </Card.Body>

  </Card>
  <Card>
    <Card.Img variant="top" src="/USPHome.png" alt="uspimg" />
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Text className="customCard">
      USP Point 3
      </Card.Text>
    </Card.Body>

  </Card>
  <Card>
    <Card.Img variant="top" src="/USPHome.png" alt="uspimg" />
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Text className="customCard">
        USP Point 4
      </Card.Text>
    </Card.Body>

  </Card>
</CardDeck>
    )
  }
}

export default Cards;
